#### 4. 定时采样任务
```java
// com/example/llmops/SafetySamplingTask.java
@Component
public class SafetySamplingTask {
    @Autowired
    private OnlineSafetyCircuitBreaker circuitBreaker;
    @Autowired
    private AiCallAuditLogMapper auditLogMapper;
    @Autowired
    private LLMEvaluator evaluator;

    // 每5分钟随机抽样1%的真实请求做安全评分
    @Scheduled(fixedRate = 300_000)
    public void sampleAndEvaluate() {
        if (circuitBreaker.getCurrentState() == CircuitState.OPEN) return;
        
        List<AiCallAuditLog> samples = auditLogMapper.randomSample(1, 30);
        for (AiCallAuditLog log : samples) {
            EvalResult result = evaluator.evaluate(log.getParsedResult());
            circuitBreaker.recordSafetyScore(result.getSafety());
        }
    }
}
```

### 验收标准
1. 连续5次安全分<9.0或单次<7.5 → 系统自动熔断，所有AI调用走规则引擎降级
2. 熔断后每10分钟自动探测，若3次探测请求安全分≥9.0 → 自动恢复正常
3. 运维群收到P0熔断告警和恢复通知
4. `/api/llmops/circuit/status`接口可查询当前熔断器状态

